name: Resonance of God Part 1: Imam Kikou - Bangor
description: When the atrocious devil tunes spread across EDM rave party scene, God saves all of his ravers out from the mess with one of God's calamity tunes named “Bangor”. Bangor sound cleansed ravers' souls from bad vibes of devil tunes that give us anarchy against the event booth, purify our heart from it, and bring back the cheerful to ravers around the world.  Bangor means chad men in Indonesian slang, a chad-ness that gives hope to ravers to combat bad vibes around any clubs & parties across the universe without hesitation.  Created by Imam Kikou & Hezn
